channel.title: Local Chapters - Where to Find Them
channel.description:
Hi all,
I am a practicing Physical Therapist located in Northern California near Sacramento.
Can someone point me in the direction of where I can find resources outlining contact info, locations, etc. of GoBabyGo! Chapters local to me?
From what I have been able to gather, there are none in this area. If that is truly the case, then I may be interested in starting a NorCal Chapter.
Thanks so much for your help! Rachel
